      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly representing the pinnacle of its class. It has been meticulously maintained, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom condition. Every component functions perfectly, offering a driving experience that feels as fresh as the day it was first manufactured.",
